<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/logo/favicon.png">
    <title>det-AI</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Concert+One&family=IBM+Plex+Serif:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @keyframes anime{
            0%{
                transform: translateX(100px);
                color: rgb(245, 242, 235);
            }
            100%{
                transform: translateX(0px);
            }
        }
        body, html {
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: "cooper", serif;
            font-weight: 100;
            font-style: normal;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .left, .right {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        

        .left {
            background-color: #b7d9db;
            width: 50vw;
        }
        .right {
            background-color: rgb(245, 242, 235);
            width: 50vw;
            
        }

        .logo {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        h1 {
            /* background-color: red; */
            animation-name: anime;
            animation-duration: 2s;
            animation-timing-function: ease-in-out;
            animation-delay: 0s;
            animation-iteration-count: 1;
            color: #4ca89e;
            font-size: 6rem;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 0px;
            margin-top: 0px;
             padding: 10px;
        }

        .line{
            border-top: 5px solid #5f6161;
            width: 65%;
            line-height: 30px;
            font-family: "Cambria";
            font-size: 18px ;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                flex-direction: column;
                height: auto;
            }
            .left, .right {
                width: 100%;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 5rem;
            }

            .buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                margin-bottom: 20vh;
            }
        }
        a.button {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 200px;
      padding: 15px 0;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 10px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      font-weight: bold;
      /* border: 2px solid #009688; */
      color: #514f4f;
      cursor: pointer;
      background-color: rgba(0, 150, 136, 0.1);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-decoration: none; /* Remove underline for links */
    }
    a.button span{
      background: #009688;
      height: 100%;
      width: 0;
      border-radius: 25px;
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      z-index: -1;
      transition: 0.5s ;
    }
    a.button:hover span{
      width: 100%;
      transform: scale(1.05);
      /* border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); */
      background-color: rgb(138, 190, 227);
      color: rgb(250, 250, 250);
    }
    a.button:hover{
      border: none;
      transform: scale(1.05);      
      /* border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); */
      background-color: rgb(138, 190, 227);
      color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
    }
    a.button:active span{
      width: 100%;
      background: #d1cdcf;
    }
    a.button:active{
      border: none;
    }
  

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="left">
            <img src="/logo/Brand.png" alt="Website Logo" class="logo" width="80%">
        </div>
        <div class="right">
            <h1 >detAI</h1>
            <p class="line">Welcome to our innovative website designed to discern the origins of any text. Are you dealing with human-written content or something generated by an AI or LLM? Simply paste your text into our scanner, and we'll instantly provide you with a detailed analysis, showing the percentage likelihood that it was written by a human versus generated by a machine.</p>
            <div>
                <a href="/login" class="button"><span></span>LOG IN</a>
                <a href="/register" class="button"><span></span>SIGN UP</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
